### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### Crear o actualizar un cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "name": "Juan Perez",
  "phone": "3001234567",
  "address": "Calle 123 # 45-67",
  "city": "Bogotá"
}

### Error de validación (Email inválido)
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "name": "Error User",
  "phone": "123"
}
